'''Liam James''' (born August 7, 1996 in [[Vancouver]], [[British Columbia]]) is a [[Canadian]] [[child actor]]. He is best known for his role as Noah Curtis in 2009 film ''[[2012 (film)|2012]]'' and for portraying [[List of Psych characters#Young Shawn|young Shawn Spencer]] on the [[USA Network]] TV series ''[[Psych]]''.
James has [[Heterochromia|one green and one blue eye.]]
